    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的电脑突遭未知病毒重度感染，杀毒软件已全部失效。下一秒，你竟化身成了你的电脑鼠标，拯救电脑免遭病毒摧毁的重任，现在便落在你的身上了！潜入文件系统深处，找出并识别引发混乱的元凶吧！</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054210/extras/855100d251fc62af92367c256cb106e8.webp?t=1766134070\" width=616 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054210/extras/4db323d0a1bd3e575f5a5257aa30f7fd.poster.avif?t=1766134070\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054210/extras/4db323d0a1bd3e575f5a5257aa30f7fd.webm?t=1766134070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054210/extras/4db323d0a1bd3e575f5a5257aa30f7fd.mp4?t=1766134070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《病毒识别：拯救系统》是一款以电脑鼠标为主角的动作肉鸽游戏，故事发生在你自己被感染的电脑操作系统中。它完美融合了弹幕地狱的疯狂操作与电脑文件系统的探索乐趣。<br><br>电脑中的文件夹化作了危机四伏的地下城，文件中隐藏着秘密、宝藏与杀机。你将穿梭于随机生成的关卡，并发掘能助你一臂之力的强大EXE程序，击退源源不断试图阻挡你前进道路的病毒。<br><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054210/extras/df147b75a90d6132b227f571f8bdd2fe.webp?t=1766134070\" width=616 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054210/extras/8efd85553cbed917fa528e626db9a562.poster.avif?t=1766134070\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054210/extras/8efd85553cbed917fa528e626db9a562.webm?t=1766134070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054210/extras/8efd85553cbed917fa528e626db9a562.mp4?t=1766134070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用多种不同风格、各具特技的可玩鼠标，在恶意病毒的围攻中杀出一条血路。每一个被腐蚀的驱动盘尽头，都有一场残酷的Boss战在等待着你。你是否已做好准备，直面强敌，将你的系统从彻底崩溃的边缘拯救回来？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054210/extras/089c426196bedd66e9c3a2ad4d7f3127.webp?t=1766134070\" width=616 height=32 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个如同地下城一般的文件系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独具一格的电脑鼠标作战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >层出不穷的随机事件，让你时刻保持警惕</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏修改词缀与多难度模式，可自由调整你的游戏体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遭遇30多种 特性各异的电脑病毒（还包括闪亮变体！）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战4场以上独特的Boss战！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁12款以上可玩鼠标</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现100多种不同的掉落战利品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集30多种能适应不同战斗风格的EXE应用程序</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的鼠标外观装饰</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >病毒图鉴，记录搜罗你已识别出的病毒</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 以及隐藏的秘密？……等待你发掘的远不止这些！</p></li></ul><br><br><br>",
